reviewText: Whole video is aerial shots from a helicopter.  What little narration there was, was done in a quiet voice that could not be heard over the music.  Tried making it louder, but that just made the music louder.  If you are going on a tour of Sicily, this will give you a good overview of all the coastal cities and an idea of what each looks like.

This is the perfect thing after a long hard day. music is beautiful, photograpy breathtaking,great for stress relief. Not a how-to tourist guide-just beautiful images of a beautiful place many people never visit. This is one to watch over and over again...
